    <mxCell id="s6_dim_lb" value="&lt;b&gt;SCD Type 2 Engine:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Read TF YAML (Dimension)&lt;br/&gt;2. SHA-256(tracked cols) → hash&lt;br/&gt;3. Compare hash to current dim&lt;br/&gt;4. New: INSERT with surrogate key&lt;br/&gt;5. Changed: expire + INSERT new&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sentinel:&lt;/b&gt; SK=-1, ID=UNKNOWN&lt;br/&gt;effective 1900-01-01 → 9999-12-31&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Dim Date:&lt;/b&gt; Full overwrite&lt;br/&gt;yyyyMMdd key, is_weekend, etc." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontColor=#1F3864;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1466" y="246" width="232" height="169" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

