      <mxGeometry x="1458" y="469" width="248" height="195" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>
    <mxCell id="s6_fact_lb" value="&lt;b&gt;Fact Engine:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Read TF YAML (Fact)&lt;br/&gt;2. SHA-256(sys‖sales_id‖date) → tx hash&lt;br/&gt;3. Temporal FK join on dim SK&lt;br/&gt;   (effective_from ≤ date ≤ effective_to)&lt;br/&gt;4. Late-arriving: FK=-1, write bridge&lt;br/&gt;5. MERGE ON transaction_hash (upsert)&lt;br/&gt;6. Partitioned by fact_batch_id&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;TF YAML covers:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;source_tables · joins · business_rules&lt;br/&gt;scd_type · target_table · dq.rules" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=8;fontColor=#1F3864;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="1466" y="477" width="232" height="179" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

